  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やーっぱり、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;のご飯が一番おいしいだぁな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As I thought, &lt;Mel&gt;'s meals really are the best~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと、ほんと、どんどん美味しくなってるよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Truly, truly, it seems to improve with every meal we have.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cooloor!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ、そうかな？　まだまだおかわりあるから、
どんどん食べてね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>D-Do you really think so? Well, there's still a lot left
so please help yourselves!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ちょい野菜多すぎじゃねーか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, isn't there TOO much veggies in here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そういうこと言う人は、食べなくてもいいから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you don't like it then just don't eat it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだ、んだ。おめぇは、食わんでもええだーよ。
その分おらが、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;の手料理ぜーんぶたいらげるだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's right! You don't have to eat if you don't like the food!
I can just help myself to your portion of &lt;Mel&gt;'s home-cooking~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>てめぇはタンスのくせに食いすぎなんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aren't you eating a WAY TOO MUCH?
You're a wardrobe!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へっへ～ん、野菜嫌いのお子ちゃまが、吠えてるだぁ。
そんなおめぇには、これで十分だーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heheh...Bark all you want you veggie-hating youth.
With how scrawny you are, this isn't even enough!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、てめぇ！　オレの肉、全部取りやがったな！
返せ！　このタンス野郎！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-You took all my meat! Give that back you
enlarged-furniture!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>肉の代わりに、たーっぷり野菜を入れてやっただど。
腹が減ってるなら、それを食えばええだ～よ～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you crying for, lad? I just swapped the meat
with vegetables. Just eat that if you're hungry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_195_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まったく食事時まで喧嘩するんだかラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Goodness, even during mealtime...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
